error.message: Class Drupal\rest_without_format\Routing\RestWithoutFormatRouteFilter implements deprecated interface Drupal\Core\Routing\RouteFilterInterface. Deprecated in drupal:8.4.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0. Instead, you should use \Drupal\Core\Routing\FilterInterface. See https://www.drupal.org/node/2894934

Parameter $request_format_route_filter of method Drupal\rest_without_format\Routing\RestWithoutFormatRouteFilter::__construct() has typehint with deprecated interface Drupal\Core\Routing\RouteFilterInterface. Deprecated in drupal:8.4.0 and is removed from drupal:9.0.0. Instead, you should use \Drupal\Core\Routing\FilterInterface. See https://www.drupal.org/node/2894934
Add core_version_requirement: ^8 || ^9 to rest_without_format.info.yml to designate that the module is compatible with Drupal 9. See https://www.drupal.org/node/3070687.
